reviewText: When I got this video I was happy to receive all the questions on the video on paper. It goes through a few different Praxis 0069 tests. The video is like a one on one with a teacher. I had a question on one of the answers and the seller took the time to explain it to me in a different personalized video. I'm not sure if this is a standard practice but he did it for me. I have never seen this before where the seller goes out of his way in that way to help a buyer. He also answered promptly. A lot of times you spend money on something and when you get the product you regret you spent money on it, but I feel the money is well spent on this product. If you are looking to become a math teacher and you have to take the Praxis 0069 or even any other Praxis, buy this!!! I will look into other videos he has on his website for future subjects.
